A lot of anons (myself included) are against stories involving intelligent feral animals due to the fact that it's getting *dangerously* close to just being feral porn, but I personally don't think anyone would have a problem with a human with a dragon largely because they're mythical, highly intelligent, and magical.
That, and there are already a few popular stories here featuring that exact premise.
